@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_eritai(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.abs(v2) - (v1 / tmp))
    tmp = (wp.abs(v0) / (wp.exp(tmp + 0.57) / (v2 + 0.22 * v2 + 0.37)))
    v2 = tmp
    v2 = 0.78
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v2 + 0.82)) - (wp.exp(v2 + 0.71) * 0.55))
    data[tid] = v0
